Global Messaging as a Platform (MaaP) Market Insights
Messaging as a Platform (MaaP) Market size was valued at USD 7.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 23.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 17.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Messaging as a Platform (MaaP) Market Overview
The global Messaging as a Platform (MaaP) market is experiencing robust growth, driven by increasing demand for efficient communication solutions across industries. The MaaP market was valued at approximately USD 20 billion in 2024 and is expected to reach around USD 45 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 14% during the forecast period. The adoption of MaaP solutions is largely driven by businesses' need for personalized, scalable, and seamless communication strategies. MaaP allows businesses to integrate messaging into their operations, enhancing customer service, engagement, and transaction capabilities, leading to widespread market adoption.

